ex_survey1: Mockup dataset of a survey.

Source: R/data.R
ex_survey1.Rd

A dataset containing fake respondents' answers to survey questions. the first two, x_sex and x_human, are intended to be independent variables, whereas the remaning are dependent. The separator between items and groups is the underscore _ (i.e. a_1-a_9 => a + 1-9) whereas the separator for labels is the hyphen. The latter corresponds with the default in SurveyXact.

Usage

ex_survey1
